1
00:00:07,674 --> 00:00:09,074
<font color="yellow">(Episode 24)</font>

2
00:00:25,134 --> 00:00:26,574
<font color="yellow">We had such a hard time finding him.</font>

3
00:00:28,574 --> 00:00:29,604
<font color="yellow">Is he the child?</font>

4
00:00:50,004 --> 00:00:51,204
<font color="yellow">Yes, he is.</font>

5
00:00:53,474 --> 00:00:55,004
<font color="yellow">It's my brother, Sang Woo.</font>

6
00:00:55,604 --> 00:00:56,634
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

7
00:00:57,604 --> 00:00:58,934
<font color="yellow">I'm glad that he's the one.</font>

8
00:01:00,174 --> 00:01:03,474
<font color="yellow">He was sent to a nearby orphanage
according to the record.</font>

9
00:01:04,904 --> 00:01:07,804
<font color="yellow">A man who went fishing found him first.</font>

10
00:01:23,204 --> 00:01:24,274
<font color="yellow">Sang Woo.</font>

11
00:01:30,374 --> 00:01:33,234
<font color="yellow">What did you just say?</font>

12
00:01:36,074 --> 00:01:37,704
<font color="yellow">Did you call me?</font>

13
00:01:39,204 --> 00:01:40,274
<font color="yellow">I think so.</font>

14
00:01:45,174 --> 00:01:47,214
<font color="yellow">What is your reason behind
your actions towards me?</font>

15
00:01:53,474 --> 00:01:54,474
<font color="yellow">Seong Joon.</font>

16
00:01:55,174 --> 00:01:56,374
<font color="yellow">What are you doing over there?</font>

17
00:01:56,874 --> 00:01:58,204
<font color="yellow">It's nothing, Father.</font>

18
00:02:09,174 --> 00:02:10,234
<font color="yellow">What were you doing?</font>

19
00:02:10,874 --> 00:02:12,334
<font color="yellow">Were you talking to someone?</font>

20
00:02:13,904 --> 00:02:14,974
<font color="yellow">No, I wasn't. Father.</font>

21
00:02:15,774 --> 00:02:17,603
<font color="yellow">- Are you throwing out the trash?
- Yes.</font>

22
00:02:17,604 --> 00:02:18,634
<font color="yellow">Let me.</font>

23
00:02:18,934 --> 00:02:20,474
<font color="yellow">Gosh, it's cold.</font>

24
00:02:22,544 --> 00:02:23,834
<font color="yellow">Let's go in, Father.</font>

25
00:03:15,534 --> 00:03:16,704
<font color="yellow">President.</font>

26
00:03:17,534 --> 00:03:18,674
<font color="yellow">Are you okay?</font>

27
00:03:18,804 --> 00:03:19,804
<font color="yellow">President.</font>

28
00:03:23,174 --> 00:03:24,204
<font color="yellow">Let's go.</font>

29
00:03:35,404 --> 00:03:36,474
<font color="yellow">Congratulations.</font>

30
00:03:37,534 --> 00:03:41,374
<font color="yellow">Your effort of 23 years has
brought you a fruitful result.</font>

31
00:03:47,134 --> 00:03:48,174
<font color="yellow">I am not so certain.</font>

32
00:03:50,904 --> 00:03:53,074
<font color="yellow">I am not certain if this
is something to celebrate.</font>

33
00:03:54,104 --> 00:03:55,534
<font color="yellow">What do you mean?</font>

34
00:03:56,474 --> 00:03:57,604
<font color="yellow">Sang Woo...</font>

35
00:03:59,534 --> 00:04:01,234
<font color="yellow">Sang Woo is with that family.</font>

36
00:04:02,634 --> 00:04:04,404
<font color="yellow">I have to bring the family to its ruins.</font>

37
00:04:05,074 --> 00:04:08,434
<font color="yellow">Would you like to revise your plan?</font>

38
00:04:09,074 --> 00:04:10,074
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

39
00:04:11,834 --> 00:04:12,834
<font color="yellow">I won't.</font>

40
00:04:14,034 --> 00:04:15,404
<font color="yellow">No, I will never revise it.</font>

41
00:04:17,004 --> 00:04:18,974
<font color="yellow">That man destroyed our family.</font>

42
00:04:19,274 --> 00:04:21,134
<font color="yellow">He drove my father to death.</font>

43
00:04:21,974 --> 00:04:24,704
<font color="yellow">He caused me to be separated
from my brother for 23 years.</font>

44
00:04:25,904 --> 00:04:28,104
<font color="yellow">Just because he raised Sang Woo,</font>

45
00:04:29,004 --> 00:04:32,274
<font color="yellow">should I forgive that man?</font>

46
00:04:32,704 --> 00:04:33,704
<font color="yellow">However,</font>

47
00:04:34,304 --> 00:04:37,344
<font color="yellow">you might harm Sang Woo. Not just
harm, but you might destroy him.</font>

48
00:04:38,344 --> 00:04:39,674
<font color="yellow">Don't you think it's possible?</font>

49
00:04:39,904 --> 00:04:42,774
<font color="yellow">Imagine he discovers that the
father, who has raised him...</font>

50
00:04:43,844 --> 00:04:46,844
<font color="yellow">for 23 years, drove his
biological father into his death.</font>

51
00:04:48,074 --> 00:04:51,374
<font color="yellow">How will Sang Woo cope with that pain?</font>

52
00:04:57,474 --> 00:04:59,604
<font color="yellow">That was the despair I felt tonight.</font>

53
00:05:00,774 --> 00:05:03,374
<font color="yellow">I couldn't even hug my
brother even if I found him.</font>

54
00:05:05,704 --> 00:05:07,974
<font color="yellow">I couldn't tell him that I was his brother.</font>

55
00:05:09,934 --> 00:05:12,474
<font color="yellow">He still has my brother.</font>

56
00:05:13,004 --> 00:05:16,074
<font color="yellow">To him, I am just a
strange and pathetic man.</font>

57
00:05:20,434 --> 00:05:22,304
<font color="yellow">I don't know how to approach him...</font>

58
00:05:24,704 --> 00:05:26,974
<font color="yellow">and how to resolve this matter.</font>

59
00:05:29,174 --> 00:05:30,534
<font color="yellow">I am clueless.</font>

60
00:05:32,474 --> 00:05:35,804
<font color="yellow">Just think about one thing tonight.</font>

61
00:05:36,404 --> 00:05:38,874
<font color="yellow">Sang Woo grew up as a fine individual.</font>

62
00:05:39,604 --> 00:05:41,034
<font color="yellow">Don't you think so?</font>

63
00:05:48,104 --> 00:05:49,474
<font color="yellow">Yes, I think so.</font>

64
00:05:51,774 --> 00:05:53,104
<font color="yellow">He did indeed.</font>

65
00:05:54,234 --> 00:05:55,274
<font color="yellow">President.</font>

66
00:05:56,704 --> 00:05:59,174
<font color="yellow">Just think about that for tonight.</font>

67
00:06:10,434 --> 00:06:11,704
<font color="yellow">Moong Chi, let's eat.</font>

68
00:06:14,074 --> 00:06:15,534
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui already fed you breakfast.</font>

69
00:06:18,804 --> 00:06:19,804
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui.</font>

70
00:06:21,274 --> 00:06:22,274
<font color="yellow">Should we go to work?</font>

71
00:06:22,734 --> 00:06:25,134
<font color="yellow">No, I will go by myself.</font>

72
00:06:25,234 --> 00:06:26,734
<font color="yellow">I will see you at work later.</font>

73
00:06:28,174 --> 00:06:29,334
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui.</font>

74
00:06:46,234 --> 00:06:47,274
<font color="yellow">Sang Woo.</font>

75
00:06:48,034 --> 00:06:49,634
<font color="yellow">Did you call me?</font>

76
00:06:50,674 --> 00:06:51,674
<font color="yellow">I think so.</font>

77
00:07:06,804 --> 00:07:07,804
<font color="yellow">Ms. Oh Dong Hui.</font>

78
00:07:08,904 --> 00:07:11,904
<font color="yellow">- Yes?
- Can you give me a cup of coffee?</font>

79
00:07:23,304 --> 00:07:24,334
<font color="yellow">Come in.</font>

80
00:07:36,474 --> 00:07:38,734
<font color="yellow">Why do you treat me like this?</font>

81
00:07:39,274 --> 00:07:40,274
<font color="yellow">Excuse me?</font>

82
00:07:41,374 --> 00:07:43,774
<font color="yellow">You know in a drama,</font>

83
00:07:43,874 --> 00:07:46,334
<font color="yellow">a woman is angry at a man.</font>

84
00:07:46,374 --> 00:07:48,004
<font color="yellow">She doesn't tell him why she's angry.</font>

85
00:07:48,604 --> 00:07:50,704
<font color="yellow">When the guy asks her why she's mad,</font>

86
00:07:50,774 --> 00:07:53,535
<font color="yellow">instead of answering, she asks him
if he doesn't know and gets angry.</font>

87
00:07:55,474 --> 00:07:58,604
<font color="yellow">How can that guy know if
she wouldn't tell him?</font>

88
00:07:59,974 --> 00:08:02,134
<font color="yellow">Why are you asking me that?</font>

89
00:08:03,174 --> 00:08:06,104
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui, aren't you angry at me?</font>

90
00:08:06,834 --> 00:08:09,634
<font color="yellow">You seem angry, but you wouldn't tell me.</font>

91
00:08:10,234 --> 00:08:13,634
<font color="yellow">You're pushing me away again.
Aren't I correct?</font>

92
00:08:13,834 --> 00:08:15,804
<font color="yellow">- No, you are wrong.
- Am I wrong?</font>

93
00:08:15,934 --> 00:08:17,134
<font color="yellow">Yes, you are wrong.</font>

94
00:08:17,974 --> 00:08:19,474
<font color="yellow">Then, why are you so distant?</font>

95
00:08:20,634 --> 00:08:22,374
<font color="yellow">What do you mean?</font>

96
00:08:23,034 --> 00:08:24,714
<font color="yellow">You said not to visit you in the workroom.</font>

97
00:08:24,804 --> 00:08:28,374
<font color="yellow">I asked you to go to work together,
but you ran away. Even now,</font>

98
00:08:28,774 --> 00:08:31,504
<font color="yellow">you were about to leave like a stray
cat after you served me coffee.</font>

99
00:08:31,874 --> 00:08:36,374
<font color="yellow">So I am certain that you are mad at me.
Are you telling me you're not?</font>

100
00:08:39,134 --> 00:08:42,634
<font color="yellow">- What?
- Don't pick a fight in the morning.</font>

101
00:08:43,374 --> 00:08:44,374
<font color="yellow">Excuse me?</font>

102
00:08:48,204 --> 00:08:50,134
<font color="yellow">If everyone's here, let's
start the meeting.</font>

103
00:08:50,504 --> 00:08:52,944
<font color="yellow">- Where's Director Han?
- He came in a while ago.</font>

104
00:08:56,904 --> 00:08:58,034
<font color="yellow">Seong Joon.</font>

105
00:08:59,804 --> 00:09:00,834
<font color="yellow">What are you doing?</font>

106
00:09:01,274 --> 00:09:04,034
<font color="yellow">Hello, Director. I'll get going now.</font>

107
00:09:10,404 --> 00:09:12,204
<font color="yellow">You're here.</font>

108
00:09:20,304 --> 00:09:23,274
<font color="yellow">- What are you doing today?
- I'm visiting the branches.</font>

109
00:09:23,404 --> 00:09:24,834
<font color="yellow">Okay. Work hard.</font>

110
00:09:33,704 --> 00:09:35,474
<font color="yellow">Ms. Hong. Pull down the blind.</font>

111
00:09:45,274 --> 00:09:47,234
<font color="yellow">The meeting with the
shareholders is next Monday.</font>

112
00:09:47,534 --> 00:09:49,074
<font color="yellow">I reckon in that meeting,</font>

113
00:09:49,104 --> 00:09:52,074
<font color="yellow">they'll discuss whether to maintain
Contents Department or not.</font>

114
00:09:52,234 --> 00:09:55,103
<font color="yellow">Before that, we must find
Writer Jo's replacement.</font>

115
00:09:55,104 --> 00:09:58,904
<font color="yellow">Not to lose our airing time, we must
submit a groundbreaking synopsis.</font>

116
00:10:00,204 --> 00:10:03,834
<font color="yellow">Did you pick three synopses
you'd like to recommend?</font>

117
00:10:03,974 --> 00:10:05,004
<font color="yellow">- Yes.
- Yes.</font>

118
00:10:05,534 --> 00:10:07,694
<font color="yellow">Can you give your recommendations
first, Director Han?</font>

119
00:10:08,474 --> 00:10:10,704
<font color="yellow">I won't partake in this.</font>

120
00:10:11,274 --> 00:10:14,134
<font color="yellow">- Why is that?
- To make sure, it's chosen fairly.</font>

121
00:10:14,734 --> 00:10:17,534
<font color="yellow">I know the titles and the
names of the writers.</font>

122
00:10:18,304 --> 00:10:20,834
<font color="yellow">Okay. Why don't we start with
you first, Mr. Park Jin Sang?</font>

123
00:10:20,874 --> 00:10:22,974
<font color="yellow">- Tell us your recommendations.
- Yes.</font>

124
00:10:29,174 --> 00:10:30,704
<font color="yellow">Seong Joon went to work early.</font>

125
00:10:30,944 --> 00:10:34,204
<font color="yellow">He said he was busy with work. He
didn't even get to have breakfast.</font>

126
00:10:34,704 --> 00:10:38,234
<font color="yellow">Did he? I guess Dong Hui
went in early as well.</font>

127
00:10:39,634 --> 00:10:44,033
<font color="yellow">I told you not to bring her up when
we are talking about Seong Joon.</font>

128
00:10:44,034 --> 00:10:46,773
<font color="yellow">Why do you talk about them together?</font>

129
00:10:46,774 --> 00:10:49,943
<font color="yellow">They work at the same company.</font>

130
00:10:49,944 --> 00:10:52,773
<font color="yellow">Even if they work at the same
company, Seong Joon is a director...</font>

131
00:10:52,774 --> 00:10:54,804
<font color="yellow">and she is just a mere employee.</font>

132
00:10:54,874 --> 00:10:58,934
<font color="yellow">How can you put them in the same
group when you talk? You're his dad.</font>

133
00:11:01,134 --> 00:11:03,774
<font color="yellow">Do you think I'm devious like you?</font>

134
00:11:04,034 --> 00:11:05,604
<font color="yellow">I didn't mean anything by it.</font>

135
00:11:05,904 --> 00:11:08,974
<font color="yellow">Anyway, watch your tongue.
Whatever you say might come true.</font>

136
00:11:10,304 --> 00:11:13,304
<font color="yellow">My gosh. Where are you going?</font>

137
00:11:14,274 --> 00:11:18,304
<font color="yellow">I'm going downstairs. Seong
Hoon didn't go to work yet.</font>

138
00:11:18,404 --> 00:11:20,324
<font color="yellow">I'm just going to give him
some beef bone broth.</font>

139
00:11:21,034 --> 00:11:22,074
<font color="yellow">How about mine?</font>

140
00:11:23,374 --> 00:11:24,474
<font color="yellow">There's none.</font>

141
00:11:28,734 --> 00:11:29,834
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

142
00:11:33,534 --> 00:11:34,634
<font color="yellow">Goodness. My head hurts.</font>

143
00:11:35,934 --> 00:11:38,174
<font color="yellow">Gosh, my head hurts so much.</font>

144
00:11:38,874 --> 00:11:39,874
<font color="yellow">My goodness.</font>

145
00:11:40,734 --> 00:11:43,634
<font color="yellow">I think I drank too much
with the Senior Secretary.</font>

146
00:11:45,874 --> 00:11:47,234
<font color="yellow">Honey.</font>

147
00:11:48,874 --> 00:11:52,374
<font color="yellow">Honey. Get me some water.</font>

148
00:11:53,504 --> 00:11:55,134
<font color="yellow">Honey.</font>

149
00:11:59,974 --> 00:12:00,974
<font color="yellow">My head.</font>

150
00:12:05,374 --> 00:12:08,334
<font color="yellow">I'm dying. Is it water with honey?</font>

151
00:12:15,474 --> 00:12:18,074
<font color="yellow">Honey. Can you get me my clothes?</font>

152
00:12:18,874 --> 00:12:21,534
<font color="yellow">I have to leave early, but
look at what I'm doing.</font>

153
00:12:22,604 --> 00:12:25,574
<font color="yellow">My gosh. I have to stop by a sauna.</font>

154
00:12:31,634 --> 00:12:33,704
<font color="yellow">Who are you?</font>

155
00:12:36,204 --> 00:12:37,604
<font color="yellow">It's me. What?</font>

156
00:12:38,234 --> 00:12:39,434
<font color="yellow">Seong Hoon?</font>

157
00:12:40,574 --> 00:12:42,834
<font color="yellow">Seong Hoon.</font>

158
00:12:43,204 --> 00:12:46,834
<font color="yellow">Why are you dressed like a wolf
in "Little Red Riding Hood"?</font>

159
00:12:48,134 --> 00:12:51,934
<font color="yellow">What? A wolf in "Little Red Riding Hood"?</font>

160
00:12:53,234 --> 00:12:55,374
<font color="yellow">Sure. I am a wolf, dressed
up as a lady. So what?</font>

161
00:12:56,734 --> 00:13:00,704
<font color="yellow">Get up. Do I need to give you water
with honey and your clothes?</font>

162
00:13:03,704 --> 00:13:04,974
<font color="yellow">Why are you flaring your nose?</font>

163
00:13:10,634 --> 00:13:11,674
<font color="yellow">Eat.</font>

164
00:13:12,374 --> 00:13:14,234
<font color="yellow">Seong Hoon, what is this?</font>

165
00:13:14,834 --> 00:13:17,934
<font color="yellow">Do you have to ask? It's leftover
fried chicken from yesterday.</font>

166
00:13:18,634 --> 00:13:19,774
<font color="yellow">But still, Seong Hoon.</font>

167
00:13:20,074 --> 00:13:23,574
<font color="yellow">Who serves leftover fried chicken
from the day before as breakfast?</font>

168
00:13:23,774 --> 00:13:26,074
<font color="yellow">Hey. Be grateful that I'm feeding you.</font>

169
00:13:26,474 --> 00:13:28,604
<font color="yellow">Our children went to school
without having breakfast.</font>

170
00:13:28,674 --> 00:13:30,574
<font color="yellow">Seong Hoon, you can't serve this.</font>

171
00:13:30,634 --> 00:13:32,474
<font color="yellow">This is ridiculous.</font>

172
00:13:32,574 --> 00:13:33,654
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

173
00:13:33,904 --> 00:13:35,034
<font color="yellow">Where is Hye Joo?</font>

174
00:13:36,034 --> 00:13:37,234
<font color="yellow">Of course, she's at work now.</font>

175
00:13:37,374 --> 00:13:40,674
<font color="yellow">Then, what about my wife?</font>

176
00:13:41,304 --> 00:13:42,674
<font color="yellow">How on earth would I know?</font>

177
00:13:47,074 --> 00:13:48,134
<font color="yellow">What are you doing here?</font>

178
00:13:49,574 --> 00:13:51,674
<font color="yellow">- Hello, Mom.
- You're here.</font>

179
00:13:51,934 --> 00:13:54,134
<font color="yellow">What are you doing?</font>

180
00:13:54,304 --> 00:13:55,304
<font color="yellow">Well...</font>

181
00:13:55,904 --> 00:13:57,133
<font color="yellow">Mom, actually...</font>

182
00:13:57,134 --> 00:13:58,774
<font color="yellow">Mom, well...</font>

183
00:13:59,134 --> 00:14:00,204
<font color="yellow">Oh, boy.</font>

184
00:14:01,034 --> 00:14:02,334
<font color="yellow">Seong Hoon!</font>

185
00:14:09,004 --> 00:14:11,433
<font color="yellow">These are the survey papers
for the demonstration.</font>

186
00:14:11,434 --> 00:14:13,374
<font color="yellow">Summarize them and make a report.</font>

187
00:14:13,534 --> 00:14:15,073
<font color="yellow">What about the spa tickets?</font>

188
00:14:15,074 --> 00:14:16,603
<font color="yellow">Find out what happened and
make a report about it.</font>

189
00:14:16,604 --> 00:14:17,774
<font color="yellow">I will.</font>

190
00:14:18,204 --> 00:14:20,373
<font color="yellow">I got a lot of calls from your family...</font>

191
00:14:20,374 --> 00:14:21,803
<font color="yellow">when you were in the showroom.</font>

192
00:14:21,804 --> 00:14:24,034
<font color="yellow">I know, my phone kept ringing.</font>

193
00:14:27,074 --> 00:14:28,504
<font color="yellow">You can leave.</font>

194
00:14:32,304 --> 00:14:34,903
<font color="yellow">Hello, my dear mother.</font>

195
00:14:34,904 --> 00:14:36,334
<font color="yellow">How are you?</font>

196
00:14:36,904 --> 00:14:38,473
<font color="yellow">Are you joking me?</font>

197
00:14:38,474 --> 00:14:40,533
<font color="yellow">Sorry? I am not.</font>

198
00:14:40,534 --> 00:14:42,174
<font color="yellow">Why did you ignore my phone calls?</font>

199
00:14:42,204 --> 00:14:43,934
<font color="yellow">I didn't, Mother.</font>

200
00:14:43,974 --> 00:14:45,204
<font color="yellow">Don't try to fool me.</font>

201
00:14:45,674 --> 00:14:48,234
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry. I was working.</font>

202
00:14:48,534 --> 00:14:52,004
<font color="yellow">You don't need to explain. What
do you think you're doing?</font>

203
00:14:52,174 --> 00:14:53,873
<font color="yellow">Pardon? What do you mean?</font>

204
00:14:53,874 --> 00:14:56,934
<font color="yellow">Don't ask me. Just come see
what your husband is doing now!</font>

205
00:14:57,304 --> 00:15:01,173
<font color="yellow">Seong Hoon, please take this
apron and this scarf off.</font>

206
00:15:01,174 --> 00:15:03,904
<font color="yellow">Wait. I'm didn't finish the housework yet.</font>

207
00:15:03,974 --> 00:15:05,404
