00:40:06,804 --> 00:40:09,374
<font color="yellow">- Go inside your room fast.
- Don't upset me more.</font>

627
00:40:09,604 --> 00:40:12,934
<font color="yellow">Be patient. My mother said I shouldn't...</font>

628
00:40:13,004 --> 00:40:15,544
<font color="yellow">act rashly if I were to do classical music.</font>

629
00:40:22,274 --> 00:40:23,504
<font color="yellow">Chang Soo!</font>

630
00:40:28,934 --> 00:40:30,004
<font color="yellow">My head hurts.</font>

631
00:40:30,604 --> 00:40:34,634
<font color="yellow">My head hurts. What's wrong with my life?</font>

632
00:40:36,434 --> 00:40:40,774
<font color="yellow">Why did our children have to be switched?</font>

633
00:40:42,074 --> 00:40:45,043
<font color="yellow">I really want to move. I want to move.</font>

634
00:40:45,044 --> 00:40:46,504
<font color="yellow">It's killing me.</font>

635
00:40:51,804 --> 00:40:53,934
<font color="yellow">Hey, where are you now?</font>

636
00:40:55,074 --> 00:40:58,874
<font color="yellow">I don't think I can go
home today, Hye Sook.</font>

637
00:40:59,204 --> 00:41:00,704
<font color="yellow">Why not? Where are you?</font>

638
00:41:01,134 --> 00:41:03,874
<font color="yellow">I'm at a Buddhist temple.</font>

639
00:41:04,544 --> 00:41:06,274
<font color="yellow">Why did you go there?</font>

640
00:41:08,004 --> 00:41:10,503
<font color="yellow">I have to bow 3,000 times today.</font>

641
00:41:10,504 --> 00:41:12,274
<font color="yellow">So please take care of the kids.</font>

642
00:41:12,474 --> 00:41:15,174
<font color="yellow">Please prepare a suit for my
husband tomorrow morning.</font>

643
00:41:15,604 --> 00:41:16,774
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

644
00:41:17,134 --> 00:41:18,734
<font color="yellow">Hee Sook!</font>

645
00:41:18,804 --> 00:41:20,074
<font color="yellow">Thank you, Hee Sook.</font>

646
00:42:10,434 --> 00:42:11,504
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

647
00:42:12,304 --> 00:42:15,074
<font color="yellow">- Hello.
- Did you come for your son?</font>

648
00:42:15,274 --> 00:42:18,204
<font color="yellow">Yes. My son is a musician.</font>

649
00:42:18,674 --> 00:42:21,304
<font color="yellow">I am praying so that he will
do well in a competition.</font>

650
00:42:21,334 --> 00:42:22,974
<font color="yellow">I see.</font>

651
00:42:23,704 --> 00:42:26,174
<font color="yellow">My son is a musician, too.</font>

652
00:42:26,734 --> 00:42:27,804
<font color="yellow">He has to...</font>

653
00:42:28,674 --> 00:42:29,974
<font color="yellow">go on a competition, too.</font>

654
00:42:31,574 --> 00:42:32,574
<font color="yellow">I see.</font>

655
00:43:08,404 --> 00:43:11,634
<font color="yellow">Moong Chi, I feel sad. Don't bother me.</font>

656
00:43:12,604 --> 00:43:14,673
<font color="yellow">I am going to bite anyone...</font>

657
00:43:14,674 --> 00:43:16,834
<font color="yellow">who bothers me today.</font>

658
00:43:17,004 --> 00:43:18,804
<font color="yellow">So don't bother me.</font>

659
00:44:12,074 --> 00:44:13,304
<font color="yellow">Pour me a drink, will you?</font>

660
00:44:19,004 --> 00:44:21,734
<font color="yellow">Do you mind if I join you?</font>

661
00:44:47,674 --> 00:44:48,674
<font color="yellow">Let me.</font>

662
00:44:50,604 --> 00:44:51,734
<font color="yellow">I'll pour you one.</font>

663
00:45:04,404 --> 00:45:05,504
<font color="yellow">This is unexpected.</font>

664
00:45:06,834 --> 00:45:08,604
<font color="yellow">I thought you hated me.</font>

665
00:45:09,174 --> 00:45:12,134
<font color="yellow">I still don't like you very much.</font>

666
00:45:17,674 --> 00:45:21,074
<font color="yellow">I feel like you're
hovering around my family.</font>

667
00:45:22,504 --> 00:45:25,504
<font color="yellow">I still have doubts about you.</font>

668
00:45:29,234 --> 00:45:30,274
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

669
00:45:34,234 --> 00:45:38,034
<font color="yellow">I thought maybe you have
something you want to say to me.</font>

670
00:45:42,874 --> 00:45:44,034
<font color="yellow">I think...</font>

671
00:45:45,174 --> 00:45:47,204
<font color="yellow">you called me that night.</font>

672
00:45:56,934 --> 00:45:57,934
<font color="yellow">Do you think so?</font>

673
00:45:59,674 --> 00:46:00,704
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

674
00:46:01,634 --> 00:46:04,104
<font color="yellow">Did I hear it wrong?</font>

675
00:46:05,804 --> 00:46:09,374
<font color="yellow">No. I called you Sang Woo.</font>

676
00:46:11,534 --> 00:46:12,604
<font color="yellow">Sang Woo...</font>

677
00:46:14,674 --> 00:46:17,374
<font color="yellow">Who is Sang Woo?</font>

678
00:46:21,774 --> 00:46:22,934
<font color="yellow">He's my brother.</font>

679
00:46:43,034 --> 00:46:45,474
<font color="yellow">- Hi, Mom.
- Where are you?</font>

680
00:46:45,574 --> 00:46:47,904
<font color="yellow">- I'm at a place near our house.
- Have you had dinner?</font>

681
00:46:50,574 --> 00:46:52,104
<font color="yellow">How are you going to eat dinner?</font>

682
00:46:52,604 --> 00:46:54,933
<font color="yellow">You should tell me how you'll eat dinner,</font>

683
00:46:54,934 --> 00:46:57,904
<font color="yellow">so I can know whether I
should fix you dinner or not.</font>

684
00:46:58,704 --> 00:47:01,274
<font color="yellow">You don't have to. I'll
go and do it myself.</font>

685
00:47:03,474 --> 00:47:06,274
<font color="yellow">I made kimchi stew today.</font>

686
00:47:06,304 --> 00:47:08,674
<font color="yellow">Come and eat it before the meat gets cold.</font>

687
00:47:09,134 --> 00:47:12,074
<font color="yellow">Okay. I will. See you soon, Mom.</font>

688
00:47:16,434 --> 00:47:17,474
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

689
00:47:20,404 --> 00:47:23,304
<font color="yellow">If you haven't had dinner
yet, you can order some food.</font>

690
00:47:23,934 --> 00:47:27,804
<font color="yellow">No. My mom says she made
kimchi stew at home.</font>

691
00:47:28,834 --> 00:47:31,004
<font color="yellow">She must've worked hard to make it.</font>

692
00:47:31,574 --> 00:47:33,804
<font color="yellow">I should go and eat it.</font>

693
00:47:36,474 --> 00:47:39,104
<font color="yellow">- I see.
- That's right.</font>

694
00:47:40,674 --> 00:47:44,874
<font color="yellow">You said your brother's
name is Sang Woo, right?</font>

695
00:47:47,334 --> 00:47:48,334
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

696
00:47:52,034 --> 00:47:53,434
<font color="yellow">Didn't I tell you before?</font>

697
00:47:54,404 --> 00:47:56,774
<font color="yellow">I have a brother who is around your age.</font>

698
00:48:04,504 --> 00:48:06,574
<font color="yellow">I lost him when I was seven years old.</font>

699
00:48:08,474 --> 00:48:09,834
<font color="yellow">His name is Lee Sang Woo.</font>

700
00:48:11,904 --> 00:48:13,534
<font color="yellow">He's the same age as you.</font>

701
00:48:17,334 --> 00:48:18,574
<font color="yellow">I see.</font>

702
00:48:20,934 --> 00:48:23,174
<font color="yellow">I moved to this neighborhood to find him,</font>

703
00:48:24,674 --> 00:48:25,774
<font color="yellow">and I found out...</font>

704
00:48:27,204 --> 00:48:29,704
<font color="yellow">you've been adopted.</font>

705
00:48:32,174 --> 00:48:33,174
<font color="yellow">That's why I...</font>

706
00:48:35,734 --> 00:48:36,934
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

707
00:48:38,804 --> 00:48:41,085
<font color="yellow">I asked you a question about
a sensitive matter abruptly.</font>

708
00:48:42,974 --> 00:48:44,004
<font color="yellow">That's what happened.</font>

709
00:48:45,904 --> 00:48:47,274
<font color="yellow">I didn't know.</font>

710
00:48:49,104 --> 00:48:51,274
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry, too.</font>

711
00:48:54,274 --> 00:48:55,304
<font color="yellow">Not at all.</font>

712
00:48:58,304 --> 00:48:59,804
<font color="yellow">I've been hoping...</font>

713
00:49:00,934 --> 00:49:04,274
<font color="yellow">my whole life that Sang Woo would have...</font>

714
00:49:06,604 --> 00:49:09,204
<font color="yellow">grown into a healthy and decent
man with a loving family...</font>

715
00:49:10,234 --> 00:49:12,104
<font color="yellow">just like you.</font>

716
00:49:15,034 --> 00:49:16,434
<font color="yellow">I guess...</font>

717
00:49:17,574 --> 00:49:20,604
<font color="yellow">that's why I called you
Sang Woo without realizing.</font>

718
00:49:21,834 --> 00:49:22,904
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

719
00:49:23,334 --> 00:49:26,674
<font color="yellow">I didn't know that was the reason
for your kindness and interest.</font>

720
00:49:31,374 --> 00:49:32,374
<font color="yellow">So,</font>

721
00:49:34,034 --> 00:49:35,834
<font color="yellow">did you find your brother?</font>

722
00:49:40,674 --> 00:49:41,934
<font color="yellow">I'm sure you will find him.</font>

723
00:49:43,004 --> 00:49:44,034
<font color="yellow">I'm also sure...</font>

724
00:49:45,104 --> 00:49:48,334
<font color="yellow">he would've grown into a
better man than I am.</font>

725
00:49:50,734 --> 00:49:52,974
<font color="yellow">- Seong Joon.
- Yes?</font>

726
00:49:53,834 --> 00:49:55,674
<font color="yellow">Are you happy with your family?</font>

727
00:49:57,604 --> 00:49:58,604
<font color="yellow">Of course.</font>

728
00:49:59,504 --> 00:50:02,534
<font color="yellow">Is there anyone who is not
happy with their family?</font>

729
00:50:05,504 --> 00:50:07,104
<font color="yellow">To me, my family is...</font>

730
00:50:08,034 --> 00:50:09,934
<font color="yellow">more valuable than my own life.</font>

731
00:50:11,974 --> 00:50:13,004
<font color="yellow">I'm sure that...</font>

732
00:50:14,074 --> 00:50:15,574
<font color="yellow">Sang Woo would be as happy as me.</font>

733
00:50:16,704 --> 00:50:17,904
<font color="yellow">Don't worry.</font>

734
00:50:51,604 --> 00:50:52,604
<font color="yellow">I think...</font>

735
00:50:53,934 --> 00:50:55,304
<font color="yellow">I lost.</font>

736
00:50:55,704 --> 00:50:58,034
<font color="yellow">What do you mean, President Lee?</font>

737
00:51:01,074 --> 00:51:02,904
<font color="yellow">I think Hyung Seop has...</font>

738
00:51:04,434 --> 00:51:05,774
<font color="yellow">defeated me.</font>

739
00:51:20,234 --> 00:51:21,274
<font color="yellow">Gosh, it hurts.</font>

740
00:51:22,774 --> 00:51:24,104
<font color="yellow">Hee Sook, what on earth...</font>

741
00:51:26,434 --> 00:51:27,734
<font color="yellow">I made...</font>

742
00:51:29,504 --> 00:51:32,174
<font color="yellow">I made 3,000 bows at the temple.</font>

743
00:51:36,074 --> 00:51:38,434
<font color="yellow">- Hee Sook. Are you okay?
- Gosh.</font>

744
00:51:39,874 --> 00:51:43,104
<font color="yellow">I think I'm going to enter nirvana soon.</font>

745
00:51:44,104 --> 00:51:47,034
<font color="yellow">You can't enter nirvana. Hold on.</font>

746
00:51:48,674 --> 00:51:49,774
<font color="yellow">My goodness.</font>

747
00:51:52,704 --> 00:51:55,304
<font color="yellow">By the way, Mother is very upset, Hee Sook.</font>

748
00:51:55,474 --> 00:51:56,934
<font color="yellow">I don't care.</font>

749
00:52:00,874 --> 00:52:03,304
<font color="yellow">Here. Look.</font>

750
00:52:03,534 --> 00:52:04,534
<font color="yellow">What's this?</font>

751
00:52:04,534 --> 00:52:05,534
<font color="yellow">(Mr. Kang)</font>

752
00:52:05,804 --> 00:52:09,034
<font color="yellow">He's the best vocal music teacher there is.</font>

753
00:52:11,734 --> 00:52:13,704
<font color="yellow">He's the best teacher in this country.</font>

754
00:52:14,304 --> 00:52:16,274
<font color="yellow">How did you get his number?</font>

755
00:52:17,534 --> 00:52:19,774
<font color="yellow">After I made 3,000 bows at the temple,</font>

756
00:52:21,004 --> 00:52:23,274
<font color="yellow">I thought I was going to die, Hye Joo.</font>

757
00:52:24,204 --> 00:52:26,873
<font color="yellow">You know I hardly make bows...</font>

758
00:52:26,874 --> 00:52:28,704
<font color="yellow">to anyone.</font>

759
00:52:28,834 --> 00:52:31,634
<font color="yellow">I do know. You're an arrogant person.</font>

760
00:52:31,674 --> 00:52:33,004
<font color="yellow">Gosh, Hye Joo.</font>

761
00:52:33,974 --> 00:52:36,934
<font color="yellow">I really...</font>

762
00:52:37,734 --> 00:52:41,574
<font color="yellow">made 3,000 bows at the temple.</font>

763
00:52:41,604 --> 00:52:43,174
<font color="yellow">- My gosh, it hurts.
- Really?</font>

764
00:52:46,674 --> 00:52:48,734
<font color="yellow">By the way, is this 6 or 8?</font>

765
00:52:48,774 --> 00:52:51,004
<font color="yellow">I think it got smudged by your sweat.</font>

766
00:52:52,674 --> 00:52:54,704
<font color="yellow">- What did you say?
- Here.</font>

767
00:53:01,174 --> 00:53:02,374
<font color="yellow">Why are you crying, Chang Soo?</font>

768
00:53:03,204 --> 00:53:07,004
<font color="yellow">Mom. Kids at school make fun of me.</font>

769
00:53:08,034 --> 00:53:09,904
<font color="yellow">Why? With what?</font>

770
00:53:10,004 --> 00:53:12,874
<font color="yellow">They say my face looks
bigger with this hair.</font>

771
00:53:13,604 --> 00:53:16,774
<font color="yellow">What? Who said that?</font>

772
00:53:17,204 --> 00:53:19,534
<font color="yellow">Who said my son's face is big?</font>

773
00:53:20,274 --> 00:53:21,274
<font color="yellow">The kids at school.</font>

774
00:53:26,434 --> 00:53:29,404
<font color="yellow">I will go and teach them a lesson.</font>

775
00:53:29,674 --> 00:53:32,074
<font color="yellow">Gosh. My son doesn't have a big face.</font>

776
00:53:32,574 --> 00:53:33,934
<font color="yellow">Don't cry.</font>

777
00:53:34,234 --> 00:53:38,273
<font color="yellow">Your face isn't big at all. My goodness.</font>

778
00:53:38,274 --> 00:53:40,234
<font color="yellow">My poor baby.</font>

779
00:53:40,404 --> 00:53:41,574
<font color="yellow">Goodness.</font>

780
00:53:42,604 --> 00:53:45,004
<font color="yellow">I should really move out of this house.</font>

781
00:53:52,804 --> 00:53:55,474
<font color="yellow">No. I must be crazy.</font>

782
00:53:55,874 --> 00:53:58,104
<font color="yellow">I guess I'm still crazy. No.</font>

783
00:54:02,534 --> 00:54:03,574
<font color="yellow">Aunt.</font>

784
00:54:03,704 --> 00:54:05,334
<font color="yellow">Yes. Hello.</font>

785
00:54:05,634 --> 00:54:07,574
<font color="yellow">Chang Soo. Come and say hello.</font>

786
00:54:07,904 --> 00:54:09,803
<font color="yellow">- Hello.
- Hi, Chang Soo.</font>

787
00:54:09,804 --> 00:54:11,204
<font color="yellow">Come and have a seat.</font>

788
00:54:11,934 --> 00:54:13,934
<font color="yellow">Here. Let's sit.</font>

789
00:54:14,174 --> 00:54:16,774
<font color="yellow">Oh, my. Hee Sook. What's wrong?</font>

790
00:54:18,004 --> 00:54:21,134
<font color="yellow">Well... It's nothing. I'm fine, Aunt.</font>

791
00:54:22,204 --> 00:54:23,234
<font color="yellow">Goodness.</font>

792
00:54:23,834 --> 00:54:26,374
<font color="yellow">Chang Soo. I heard that you
study vocal music now.</font>

793
00:54:26,674 --> 00:54:28,504
<font color="yellow">- Yes.
- My gosh.</font>

794
00:54:28,704 --> 00:54:31,474
<font color="yellow">I've never imagined that
you'd study singing.</font>

795
00:54:32,904 --> 00:54:34,404
<font color="yellow">That makes two of us.</font>

796
00:54:35,834 --> 00:54:38,704
<font color="yellow">That's right. Have you found a teacher yet?</font>

797
00:54:38,974 --> 00:54:42,174
<font color="yellow">I don't think Professor Park can teach you.</font>

798
00:54:42,734 --> 00:54:44,674
<font color="yellow">You're right. That's why...</font>

799
00:54:44,904 --> 00:54:46,633
<font color="yellow">I think I will let him teach Chang Soo.</font>

800
00:54:46,634 --> 00:54:48,574
<font color="yellow">I was wondering if you know him.</font>

801
00:54:50,474 --> 00:54:52,904
<font color="yellow">Well, he's not such a great teacher.</font>

802
00:54:54,774 --> 00:54:57,833
<font color="yellow">Wait. Why not? Among other parents,</font>

803
00:54:57,834 --> 00:55:00,634
<font color="yellow">he's considered as the best teacher.</font>

804
00:55:00,774 --> 00:55:03,874
<font color="yellow">It was so hard for me to get his number.</font>

805
00:55:05,234 --> 00:55:07,973
<font color="yellow">People like you who don't know him well...</font>

806
00:55:07,974 --> 00:55:10,604
<font color="yellow">would think that he is a great teacher.</font>

807
00:55:10,934 --> 00:55:12,634
<font color="yellow">But the way I see it,</font>

808
00:55:13,534 --> 00:55:16,533
<font color="yellow">everyone is just mediocre except for...</font>

809
00:55:16,534 --> 00:55:18,074
<font color="yellow">one man.</font>

810
00:55:18,874 --> 00:55:21,174
<font color="yellow">One man? Who is that?</font>

811
00:55:23,034 --> 00:55:24,134
<font color="yellow">He was...</font>

812
00:55:25,234 --> 00:55:27,074
<font color="yellow">the best singer I've ever known.</font>

813
00:55:28,204 --> 00:55:30,274
<font color="yellow">Oh, my. Who is it?</font>

814
00:55:30,634 --> 00:55:33,933
<font color="yellow">Just someone I know. Stop asking.
It's painful to talk about him.</font>

815
00:55:33,934 --> 00:55:36,004
<font color="yellow">Just let Mr. Kang teach Chang Soo.</font>

816
00:55:37,034 --> 00:55:38,354
<font color="yellow">"It's painful to talk about him"?</font>

817
00:55:39,034 --> 00:55:41,573
<font color="yellow">If Chang Soo is going to
work as a singer in Korea,</font>

818
00:55:41,574 --> 00:55:43,104
<font color="yellow">Mr. Kang won't be a bad teacher.</font>

819
00:55:43,234 --> 00:55:45,104
<font color="yellow">I just have high standards.</font>

820
00:55:45,534 --> 00:55:48,533
<font color="yellow">Aunt. Who is that man?
Tell me more about him.</font>

821
00:55:48,534 --> 00:55:49,904
<font color="yellow">Forget it.</font>

822
00:56:00,434 --> 00:56:02,904
<font color="yellow">Gosh, Aunt. Come on.</font>

823
00:56:03,104 --> 00:56:06,174
<font color="yellow">Who is the man you just mentioned?</font>

824
00:56:06,704 --> 00:56:08,674
<font color="yellow">Could you please tell me? Please.</font>

825
00:56:09,474 --> 00:56:10,874
<font color="yellow">Stop bothering me.</font>

826
00:56:11,074 --> 00:56:13,374
<font color="yellow">I'm listening to music. Be quiet.</font>

827
00:56:15,174 --> 00:56:17,134
<font color="yellow">Aunt. Please tell me who he is.</font>

828
00:56:57,634 --> 00:56:58,704
<font color="yellow">Hello?</font>

829
00:56:58,904 --> 00:57:00,374
<font color="yellow">Can I see you for a second?</font>

830
00:57:12,734 --> 00:57:15,104
<font color="yellow">I'm surprised that you let
me come into your workroom.</font>

831
00:57:18,704 --> 00:57:19,834
<font color="yellow">How...</font>

832
00:57:20,304 --> 00:57:23,474
<font color="yellow">could you do such thing without
discussing it with me?</font>

833
00:57:23,734 --> 00:57:25,833
<font color="yellow">- Dong Hui.
- You know better than anyone...</font>

834
00:57:25,834 --> 00:57:27,874
<font color="yellow">that I've worked so hard to write...</font>

835
00:57:27,904 --> 00:57:29,374
<font color="yellow">each and every word of it.</font>

836
00:57:29,534 --> 00:57:31,334
<font color="yellow">How could you do such a thing?</font>

837
00:57:31,804 --> 00:57:34,734
<font color="yellow">Why did you use my script
without asking me first?</font>

838
00:57:34,934 --> 00:57:37,704
<font color="yellow">Why did you sell my baby
without my approval?</font>

839
00:57:38,174 --> 00:57:39,204
<font color="yellow">How is it...</font>

840
00:57:39,574 --> 00:57:41,204
<font color="yellow">just your baby?</font>

841
00:57:41,474 --> 00:57:44,034
<font color="yellow">I also helped that script grow.</font>

842
00:57:44,134 --> 00:57:45,134
<font color="yellow">Even so,</font>

843
00:57:45,604 --> 00:57:47,804
<font color="yellow">you didn't have to do that.</font>

844
00:57:47,934 --> 00:57:51,834
<font color="yellow">Now people say I'm debuting because
of you, not because of my work.</font>

845
00:57:52,704 --> 00:57:54,534
<font color="yellow">Are you complaining about it?</font>

846
00:57:55,474 --> 00:57:57,373
<font color="yellow">I chose good synopses among...</font>

847
00:57:57,374 --> 00:57:59,534
<font color="yellow">the ones I had, and gave
them out to the team.</font>

848
00:57:59,934 --> 00:58:03,004
<font color="yellow">We took a vote, and your work was chosen.</font>

849
00:58:03,334 --> 00:58:05,504
<font color="yellow">I never forced anyone to pick yours.</font>

850
00:58:06,034 --> 00:58:09,103
<font color="yellow">I'm asking why you included
mine along with those...</font>

851
00:58:09,104 --> 00:58:10,634
<font color="yellow">great synopses.</font>

852
00:58:10,704 --> 00:58:13,533
<font color="yellow">They picked yours without
realizing that it's yours.</font>

853
00:58:13,534 --> 00:58:15,474
<font color="yellow">If they had known, they
wouldn't have picked it.</font>

854
00:58:15,704 --> 00:58:17,134
<font color="yellow">They know they shouldn't.</font>

855
00:58:17,334 --> 00:58:18,433
<font color="yellow">What did you say?</font>

856
00:58:18,434 --> 00:58:20,634
<font color="yellow">Why are you so insecure
about your own work?</font>

857
00:58:20,904 --> 00:58:24,474
<font color="yellow">You call it your baby. How could
you have such little trust in it?</font>

858
00:58:24,774 --> 00:58:26,304
<font color="yellow">- Look.
- Also,</font>

859
00:58:26,534 --> 00:58:29,034
<font color="yellow">who says I helped you make your debut?</font>

860
00:58:29,334 --> 00:58:32,173
<font color="yellow">Does that mean I helped
you debut because...</font>

861
00:58:32,174 --> 00:58:34,274
<font color="yellow">I want to get on the right side of you?</font>

862
00:58:34,974 --> 00:58:36,134
<font color="yellow">Why would I?</font>

863
00:58:37,404 --> 00:58:39,704
<font color="yellow">Why do I have to try to be in your favor?</font>

864
00:58:40,074 --> 00:58:41,304
<font color="yellow">What did you say?</font>

865
00:58:41,474 --> 00:58:43,204
<font color="yellow">This is so insulting.</font>

866
00:58:43,834 --> 00:58:46,174
<font color="yellow">What do you all take me for?</font>

867
00:58:46,704 --> 00:58:50,174
<font color="yellow">I'm confident that I'm
a competent producer.</font>

868
00:58:50,274 --> 00:58:54,134
<font color="yellow">Even if they give me 100 beautiful
actresses like Scarlett Johansson,</font>

869
00:58:54,434 --> 00:58:55,903
<font color="yellow">I would never trade it...</font>

870
00:58:55,904 --> 00:58:58,303
<font color="yellow">with one great script.</font>

871
00:58:58,304 --> 00:58:59,934
<font color="yellow">- Do you get it?
- My gosh.</font>

872
00:59:00,774 --> 00:59:03,574
<font color="yellow">Anyhow, I will never do it.
I wanted to let you know.</font>

873
00:59:03,674 --> 00:59:04,734
<font color="yellow">Forget it, then.</font>

874
00:59:04,904 --> 00:59:07,033
<font color="yellow">You're kicking away your own fortune.</font>

875
00:59:07,034 --> 00:59:09,334
<font color="yellow">A great opportunity comes
along, but you don't take it.</font>

876
00:59:09,374 --> 00:59:10,704
<font color="yellow">Suit yourself, then.</font>

877
00:59:12,234 --> 00:59:13,274
<font color="yellow">Hey!</font>

878
00:59:13,374 --> 00:59:15,474
<font color="yellow">Did you just yell at me?</font>

879
00:59:15,534 --> 00:59:17,734
<font color="yellow">Yes, I did. What are you going to do?</font>

880
00:59:17,804 --> 00:59:19,173
<font color="yellow">My gosh. Hey!</font>

881
00:59:19,174 --> 00:59:20,174
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

882
00:59:34,474 --> 00:59:35,674
<font color="yellow">Aren't you going to eat lunch?</font>

883
00:59:37,104 --> 00:59:38,404
<font color="yellow">I'm just going to take a rest.</font>

884
00:59:40,774 --> 00:59:43,934
<font color="yellow">Are you getting ready for the
stockholders' meeting tomorrow?</font>

885
00:59:44,104 --> 00:59:45,634
<font color="yellow">Please get out.</font>

886
00:59:55,534 --> 00:59:57,134
<font color="yellow">Lunch is ready, Sir.</font>

887
00:59:59,074 --> 01:00:01,674
<font color="yellow">Gosh. It's bean paste stew again.</font>

888
01:00:03,274 --> 01:00:06,174
<font color="yellow">I like bean paste stew very much.</font>

889
01:00:08,074 --> 01:00:10,373
<font color="yellow">How long have you been
working in our house?</font>

890
01:00:10,374 --> 01:00:12,274
<font color="yellow">It's been five years.</font>

891
01:00:13,134 --> 01:00:14,404
<font color="yellow">It hasn't been that long.</font>

892
01:00:14,934 --> 01:00:18,534
<font color="yellow">We once had a housekeeper who
worked here for 20 years.</font>

893
01:00:20,274 --> 01:00:22,734
<font color="yellow">She made...</font>

894
01:00:22,934 --> 01:00:25,474
<font color="yellow">such delicious bean paste stew.</font>

895
01:00:27,604 --> 01:00:28,634
<font color="yellow">President Bang.</font>

896
01:00:29,334 --> 01:00:30,404
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

897
01:00:32,974 --> 01:00:35,374
<font color="yellow">So, how did it go?</font>

898
01:00:41,674 --> 01:00:42,734
<font color="yellow">Is that so?</font>

899
01:00:44,234 --> 01:00:46,404
<font color="yellow">I said I'll fold it for you.</font>

900
01:00:46,774 --> 01:00:48,434
<font color="yellow">Just eat your tangerines.</font>

901
01:00:49,134 --> 01:00:52,134
<font color="yellow">I'll fold my own laundry.</font>

902
01:00:53,104 --> 01:00:56,504
<font color="yellow">I know that you're bothered
that I'm living off you.</font>

903
01:00:56,804 --> 01:00:59,634
<font color="yellow">I can imagine what you're going to say...</font>

904
01:00:59,674 --> 01:01:02,173
<font color="yellow">if I ask you to fold my laundry.</font>

905
01:01:02,174 --> 01:01:04,134
<font color="yellow">Why would I hear that?</font>

906
01:01:05,534 --> 01:01:09,604
<font color="yellow">Is it because of what my
daughter-in-law said the other day?</font>

907
01:01:11,534 --> 01:01:13,804
<font color="yellow">Forget about what she said.</font>

908
01:01:14,174 --> 01:01:17,404
<font color="yellow">She didn't mean it in a bad way.</font>

909
01:01:18,004 --> 01:01:21,273
<font color="yellow">She was just worried that
Dong Hui should marry...</font>

910
01:01:21,274 --> 01:01:22,634
<font color="yellow">That's my point.</font>

911
01:01:22,974 --> 01:01:25,203
<font color="yellow">Why would your family worry about...</font>

912
01:01:25,204 --> 01:01:27,434
<font color="yellow">whom my granddaughter will marry?</font>

913
01:01:27,574 --> 01:01:30,833
<font color="yellow">They're not just my family.
You shouldn't say that.</font>

914
01:01:30,834 --> 01:01:34,004
<font color="yellow">We've been living in the
same roof for months now.</font>

915
01:01:34,504 --> 01:01:38,074
<font color="yellow">People don't even treat
their dog so coldheartedly.</font>

916
01:01:38,304 --> 01:01:41,074
<font color="yellow">Are you likening Dong Hui to a dog now?</font>

917
01:01:41,134 --> 01:01:42,833
<font color="yellow">Like your dog, Moong Chi?</font>

918
01:01:42,834 --> 01:01:45,033
<font color="yellow">Why do you always get upset whenever...</font>

919
01:01:45,034 --> 01:01:46,704
<font color="yellow">we talk about Dong Hui?</font>

920
01:01:47,004 --> 01:01:49,874
<font color="yellow">My goodness. I don't understand.</font>

921
01:01:52,104 --> 01:01:54,074
<font color="yellow">Forget it. Forget I said anything.</font>

922
01:01:55,004 --> 01:01:58,334
<font color="yellow">By the way, you said Dong Hui was...</font>

923
01:01:59,034 --> 01:02:02,534
<font color="yellow">the granddaughter of your brother, right?</font>

924
01:02:02,804 --> 01:02:05,333
<font color="yellow">His son and son's wife suddenly died...</font>

925
01:02:05,334 --> 01:02:06,504
<font color="yellow">in an accident.</font>

926
01:02:06,674 --> 01:02:09,604
<font color="yellow">You said that's why you
started to raise Dong Hui.</font>

927
01:02:10,604 --> 01:02:13,673
<font color="yellow">Why are you so interested in Dong Hui?</font>

928
01:02:13,674 --> 01:02:15,554
<font color="yellow">What do you want to know
about my dear Dong Hui?</font>

929
01:02:15,604 --> 01:02:17,634
<font color="yellow">Why are you getting so angry?</font>

930
01:02:18,174 --> 01:02:21,633
<font color="yellow">I just thought maybe I can
fix her up with someone.</font>

931
01:02:21,634 --> 01:02:23,503
<font color="yellow">If you want to fix someone up,</font>

932
01:02:23,504 --> 01:02:25,534
<font color="yellow">you should fix up your
60-year-old daughter.</font>

933
01:02:25,704 --> 01:02:26,704
<font color="yellow">What did you say?</font>

934
01:02:26,974 --> 01:02:29,634
<font color="yellow">Are you attacking my weak spot?</font>

935
01:02:30,274 --> 01:02:33,103
<font color="yellow">I'm only saying this because you keep...</font>

936
01:02:33,104 --> 01:02:35,234
<font color="yellow">talking about Dong Hui.</font>

937
01:02:35,334 --> 01:02:38,833
<font color="yellow">We have a man and a woman who
are at a marriageable age.</font>

938
01:02:38,834 --> 01:02:40,903
<font color="yellow">Isn't it natural that...</font>

939
01:02:40,904 --> 01:02:43,874
<font color="yellow">we talk about their marriage?</font>

940
01:02:44,204 --> 01:02:45,534
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui isn't...</font>

941
01:02:46,074 --> 01:02:49,373
<font color="yellow">someone I can give away to
anybody just because...</font>

942
01:02:49,374 --> 01:02:51,734
<font color="yellow">she's old enough to marry.</font>

943
01:02:51,904 --> 01:02:53,474
<font color="yellow">You shouldn't...</font>

944
01:02:53,634 --> 01:02:56,934
<font color="yellow">treat her this way just because
she doesn't have parents.</font>

945
01:02:58,304 --> 01:03:01,234
<font color="yellow">It's not like she's from
a rich family. Gosh.</font>

946
01:03:01,834 --> 01:03:04,873
<font color="yellow">Whether you have parents or not,
you marry someone eventually.</font>

947
01:03:04,874 --> 01:03:07,273
<font color="yellow">Why do you think Dong Hui is so special?</font>

948
01:03:07,274 --> 01:03:08,834
<font color="yellow">How ridiculous.</font>

949
01:03:10,974 --> 01:03:14,674
<font color="yellow">Anyhow, don't speak inappropriately
just because we live together.</font>

950
01:03:15,174 --> 01:03:18,634
<font color="yellow">My goodness. Why don't you stop
being inappropriate first?</font>

951
01:03:20,034 --> 01:03:22,504
<font color="yellow">Excuse me? What are you talking about?</font>

952
01:03:22,674 --> 01:03:24,134
<font color="yellow">Why am I being appropriate?</font>

953
01:03:24,274 --> 01:03:27,234
<font color="yellow">Did you think I wouldn't know?
You're seeing a man.</font>

954
01:03:28,004 --> 01:03:29,034
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

955
01:03:29,404 --> 01:03:30,434
<font color="yellow">It's true.</font>

956
01:03:30,504 --> 01:03:32,034
<font color="yellow">Do you think I don't know about it?</font>

957
01:03:32,234 --> 01:03:35,404
<font color="yellow">Gosh, every night,</font>

958
01:03:35,534 --> 01:03:37,634
<font color="yellow">you hide and talk to a guy.</font>

959
01:03:38,474 --> 01:03:40,604
<font color="yellow">You are so secretive about it...</font>

960
01:03:40,704 --> 01:03:43,603
<font color="yellow">that you won't even introduce his
friend to your lonely friend.</font>

961
01:03:43,604 --> 01:03:45,104
<font color="yellow">You enjoy it alone.</font>

962
01:03:45,204 --> 01:03:48,303
<font color="yellow">I shared everything with you,
no matter how small it is.</font>

963
01:03:48,304 --> 01:03:49,404
<font color="yellow">Do you know that?</font>

964
01:03:49,904 --> 01:03:52,574
<font color="yellow">What did you say?</font>

965
01:03:52,604 --> 01:03:56,534
<font color="yellow">They say sorrow reduces to half and
joy doubles when you share it.</font>

966
01:03:57,174 --> 01:04:00,633
<font color="yellow">I still can't get my head around...</font>

967
01:04:00,634 --> 01:04:02,634
<font color="yellow">about why men find you so charming.</font>

968
01:04:03,204 --> 01:04:06,204
<font color="yellow">You always say you won't marry off
your daughter-in-law to anyone,</font>

969
01:04:06,234 --> 01:04:08,634
<font color="yellow">and you lock her in a
room in her prime time.</font>

970
01:04:08,674 --> 01:04:11,834
<font color="yellow">Yet you always talk on the
phone with your boyfriend.</font>

971
01:04:12,304 --> 01:04:14,304
<font color="yellow">I wouldn't care if you worked
at a building as a cleaner...</font>

972
01:04:14,474 --> 01:04:16,334
<font color="yellow">or if you went to a skating link...</font>

973
01:04:16,474 --> 01:04:20,134
<font color="yellow">and broke your arm.</font>

974
01:04:20,434 --> 01:04:23,104
<font color="yellow">What did you say? How dare you?</font>

975
01:04:24,504 --> 01:04:27,704
<font color="yellow">- Gosh, I am so upset.
- Goodness, Mother.</font>

976
01:04:29,274 --> 01:04:30,834
<font color="yellow">Why didn't you invite me to lunch?</font>

977
01:04:30,874 --> 01:04:33,204
<font color="yellow">- Goodness.
- Did you not eat yet?</font>

978
01:04:33,304 --> 01:04:35,603
<font color="yellow">- Have a seat, Mother.
- Nobody gave me food.</font>

979
01:04:35,604 --> 01:04:37,504
<font color="yellow">Have a seat, Mother, I
will serve it to you.</font>

980
01:04:38,634 --> 01:04:41,233
<font color="yellow">Why didn't you have lunch with Gui Boon?</font>

981
01:04:41,234 --> 01:04:44,174
<font color="yellow">Don't even mention her to me.
I really don't like her.</font>

982
01:04:44,804 --> 01:04:46,204
<font color="yellow">Did something happen?</font>

983
01:04:46,234 --> 01:04:49,274
<font color="yellow">I offered to match her granddaughter,</font>

984
01:04:49,304 --> 01:04:52,573
<font color="yellow">and she yelled at me saying
that her granddaughter...</font>

985
01:04:52,574 --> 01:04:55,004
<font color="yellow">won't marry just anyone.</font>

986
01:04:55,034 --> 01:04:57,574
<font color="yellow">- What?
- Is that true?</font>

987
01:04:57,674 --> 01:05:01,574
<font color="yellow">It is. Does she think her
granddaughter is precious,</font>

988
01:05:01,704 --> 01:05:03,374
<font color="yellow">and my grandson is not?</font>

989
01:05:03,474 --> 01:05:05,774
<font color="yellow">Is that what she thinks?</font>

990
01:05:06,634 --> 01:05:10,474
<font color="yellow">I hate old people who think their
grandchild is the most precious.</font>

991
01:05:11,234 --> 01:05:14,704
<font color="yellow">I really think that way of
thinking should be eradicated.</font>

992
01:05:15,374 --> 01:05:19,104
<font color="yellow">Didn't you say that Dong Hui had
a rather unfortunate childhood?</font>

993
01:05:19,404 --> 01:05:20,804
<font color="yellow">I think that's what I heard.</font>

994
01:05:20,834 --> 01:05:22,803
<font color="yellow">I heard she's the child of...</font>

995
01:05:22,804 --> 01:05:24,934
<font color="yellow">Gui Boon's brother's son.</font>

996
01:05:25,104 --> 01:05:27,703
<font color="yellow">The family got into an accident,
and only Dong Hui survived.</font>

997
01:05:27,704 --> 01:05:29,734
<font color="yellow">That's why Gui Boon raised her.</font>

998
01:05:30,404 --> 01:05:32,734
<font color="yellow">Goodness, did that really happen?</font>

999
01:05:32,904 --> 01:05:36,103
<font color="yellow">Yes. That's why Gui Boon
is overprotecting her.</font>

1000
01:05:36,104 --> 01:05:37,904
<font color="yellow">She thinks her granddaughter
is the most precious one.</font>

1001
01:05:38,074 --> 01:05:39,674
<font color="yellow">I hate her so much.</font>

1002
01:05:41,004 --> 01:05:43,404
<font color="yellow">Calm down and have some sujebi.</font>

1003
01:05:44,374 --> 01:05:47,734
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui's born with a
life fitting for a writer.</font>

1004
01:05:47,874 --> 01:05:49,904
<font color="yellow">Her life is full of stories.</font>

1005
01:05:50,404 --> 01:05:53,234
<font color="yellow">- Stop it.
- What?</font>

1006
01:06:02,574 --> 01:06:05,034
<font color="yellow">- Hello, Madam.
- Goodness.</font>

1007
01:06:11,504 --> 01:06:12,604
<font color="yellow">Mom!</font>

1008
01:06:13,874 --> 01:06:16,434
<font color="yellow">Mom, it's me, Bang Jin.</font>

1009
01:06:17,234 --> 01:06:19,304
<font color="yellow">It's been such a long time.</font>

1010
01:06:20,674 --> 01:06:23,534
<font color="yellow">You look the same, Mom.</font>

1011
01:06:38,934 --> 01:06:39,934
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

1012
01:06:41,074 --> 01:06:42,174
<font color="yellow">It's ready.</font>

1013
01:07:13,134 --> 01:07:14,174
<font color="yellow">Sir?</font>

1014
01:07:16,734 --> 01:07:18,774
<font color="yellow">- Let's go.
- Okay.</font>

1015
01:07:37,304 --> 01:07:40,474
<font color="yellow">Sir, it's Jeong Eun. What should I do?</font>

1016
01:07:49,304 --> 01:07:50,404
<font color="yellow">Let's just go.</font>

1017
01:08:09,804 --> 01:08:10,874
<font color="yellow">Hyun Woo.</font>

1018
01:08:11,474 --> 01:08:13,104
<font color="yellow">Are you home, Hyun Woo?</font>

1019
01:08:17,734 --> 01:08:20,704
<font color="yellow">Where did he go? He's not
picking up his phone, either.</font>

1020
01:08:27,104 --> 01:08:28,344
<font color="yellow">(Han Jeong Eun)</font>

1021
01:09:00,844 --> 01:09:02,704
<font color="yellow">(Father, I'll Take Care of You)</font>

1022
01:09:03,174 --> 01:09:04,174
<font color="yellow">Hyeon Jung?</font>

1023
01:09:05,034 --> 01:09:07,134
<font color="yellow">It's the late Gwang Ho's daughter.</font>

1024
01:09:07,504 --> 01:09:09,634
<font color="yellow">- Hello.
- Hello.</font>

1025
01:09:10,234 --> 01:09:12,844
<font color="yellow">- How dare you come here?
- Is Seong Joon well?</font>

1026
01:09:13,134 --> 01:09:14,534
<font color="yellow">How much did it drop?</font>

1027
01:09:14,844 --> 01:09:18,674
<font color="yellow">I don't think I can get
away from Mom, Uncle.</font>

1028
01:09:19,504 --> 01:09:21,074
<font color="yellow">I was truthful.</font>

1029
01:09:21,474 --> 01:09:23,344
<font color="yellow">I treated you sincerely.</font>

